<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الشَّمْسِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٠٦:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وَالْأَرْضِ وَمَا طَحَاهَا <span class="c2">(٦)</span> وَنَفْسٍ وَمَا سَوَّاهَا <span class="c2">(٧)</span> فَأَلْهَمَهَا فُجُورَهَا وَتَقْوَاهَا <span class="c2">(٨)</span> قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَنْ زَكَّاهَا <span class="c2">(٩)</span> وَقَدْ خَابَ مَنْ دَسَّاهَا <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>} <span class="c4">[الشمس: ٦ - ١٠]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{طَحَاهَا}</span>: <span class="c2">«دَحَاهَا»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٨ص١٢٥:</span> قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ: <span class="c3">{دَسَّاهَا}</span>: أَغْوَاهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>